				<title>+1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13508077/scp-5620#post-4809685</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 02 Nov 2020 12:45:18 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ADudeCalledLeo</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6881864</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Pretty cool.</p> <p>The question is, does 5620 uncover wrongdoing or <em>cause</em> it? Was Researcher Thomas an infiltrator from the CI or was he a real Foundation employee driven mad?</p> <p>Apparently the folklore implies the former, but who knows? Documentation of mind-affecting skips is inherently untrustworthy.</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">or maybe I'm just reading too much into it, who knows</span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
