					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13508077#post-4719498</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13508077/scp-5620#post-4719498</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2020 20:02:41 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>PlaguePJP</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5813664</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>That’s fair, however I’ll explain my reasoning for including an insurgency reference. In folklore this creature is a gossip and exposes wrongdoing done by the village people. So I decided to twist that into it uncovering a small coup in the Foundation.</p> <p>Thanks for reading!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
